originalText.text: Avoid if you care about your cars paint. Parked my newly purchased here for a month and every time I would pick it up it would have new scratches. Staff is told me that it was already scratched when I took it. Even though it was a new car and Was not used much during the time it parked there. At the end I had to cancel my membership because they were ruining my brand new car.

originalText.text: Good place to leave your car. They have security cameras to review any previous scratches from your vehicle. They do that with you so that when you come back you don’t think they did it. I found that to be pretty smart. Prices overnight are $25 per day/night. A little pricey but it’s the standard in the area. Very good service as well.
